    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>
                <date>June 23<hi rend="sup">rd</hi> 1862</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. Isaac. Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Enclosed please<lb/> find $3, which please and place to our<lb/>
                credit for the Occident.</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">Yours Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <persName role="author">Samuels Hoffman</persName>
            </p>
            <p>P.S. <persName>Mr T. Haasah</persName> from <placeName>Louisville Ky</placeName><lb/>
                who is a friend of ours, has written So<lb/> as and requested as, So inquire as
                    <placeName>Phi<lb/>ladelphia</placeName>, <sic>wheser</sic> a woman who is
                about<lb/> 55 <sic>jears</sic> old and who has the best of<lb/>
                <sic>recomodations</sic>, would be accepted in<lb/> the jewish foster home of your
                City,<lb/> the woman in reference, is stout and<lb/> hardy, but to religious to
                agree in<lb/> a private<add>?</add> family of <placeName>Louisville</placeName>.<lb/>
                <persName>Mr Haasah</persName> wishes to know under<lb/> what rules and regulations
                she would<lb/> be accepted, and what kind of work<lb/> she would have to do. Knowing
                Sir<lb/> that you and conversant with these<lb/> affairs, we take the liberty to
                request</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p>you, so either answer us the above<lb/> questions or to <persName>Mr Th.
                    Haasah</persName> of<lb/>
                <placeName>Louisville Ky</placeName>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <persName role="author">S. H.</persName>
            </p>
            <p>We omitted to mention, that the<lb/> woman is poor.</p>
        </body>
